data.name: label1.Text
data.value:
1. If you are a new user first register yourself by clicking at Register button
2. While registering yourself Fill all the information carefully
3. Must remember the email and password you have entered as they will be your credentials to login
4. After registering successfully you can go to the login page
5. Login yourself and go to the menu page where you can find the variety of subjects to play/practise in
6. Choose any subject as per your need and start playing
7. Make sure you have read the game rules carefully before playing the game

data.name: label2.Text
data.value:
1. There will be multiple levels in each subject , you can go to the next level only after clearing current level
2. Each level contains total 10 questions
3. Player will get 1 minute for every question
4. With every correct answer you will get 5 points
5. If you answer the question correctly within 20 seconds then you will be rewarded with 3 bonus points
6. Toughness of the questions will be increased with each higher level
7. In each level you will have total 4 lifelines
